headline: Buy Online, Avoid People? GoDaddy Survey Uncovers New Gen Z & Millennial Shopping Habits
summary: A new survey by GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) found the latest quirky shopping habits Gen Z and Millennials have adopted are changing the landscape of commerce — with some possibly unintended consequences.
